HtmlItemData.Html:
General Practice Survey
 
Dear patient, we value your opinions.  In order to make improvements in our practice, we would appreciate you taking the time to complete this survey.  Your responses will be confidential.
We are interested in any other comments you may have.  Please use the space below.

ItemTexts_SingleLineTextItemData.TextValue: The doctor I saw today was Dr:

ItemTexts_Select1Data.TextValue: How many times have you seen a doctor from your practice in the last 12 months?
How do you feel you are treated by receptionists at your practice?
Do you feel the practice opening hours are acceptable?
Regarding the times you wish to see a PARTICULAR doctor, how quickly do you usually get to see that doctor?
How do you feel about this?
Regarding the times you are happy to see ANY doctor, how quickly do you usually get seen?
How do you feel about this?
If you need to see a doctor urgently, are you able to get an appointment that day?
Have you ever been offered a phone consultation if you are not able to schedule an emergency appointment for that day?
How long do you usually sit in the waiting room before being called for your consultation?
How do you feel about this?
With regards to the times you have phoned the practice, how do you rate the ability to get through to reception?
With regards to the times you have phoned the practice, how do you rate the ability to speak to a doctor for medical advice or if you have a question?
In general, how often do you see your assigned doctor?
(This question refers to your assigned doctor. If you don't have an assigned doctor, apply your answer to the doctor you know best at the practice).
How do you feel about this?
We have some optional personal questions that will help us understand your answers more, would you like to answer them?
What is your gender?
What is your age?
Do you have any long-standing illness, disability or infirmity?
(by this we mean anything that has troubled you over a period of time or that is likely to affect you over a period of time)
Is your accommodation:
Which of the following best describes you?
Other (please specify):
